726887f-a.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - 198th Street
726887f-a.text:
Hollis Ave., south side, between 198th and 199th Streets,
showing the Charles De Bevoise farmhouse.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

726888f-b.title: Queens: Hollis Avenue - 198th Street
726888f-b.text:
Hollis Ave., north side, between 198th and 200th Sts., showing
in a set of two views, the Oldfield Hendrickson house. IIt was occupied
by the Hendrickson family from 1860 to 1908, when Walter Horn bought
it in 1908. He still occupied it in 1923.
May 1923.
Views 1 and 2.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
